00:07:00,790 --> 00:07:02,459
Lights, please.

00:07:02,459 --> 00:07:04,527
Means we're not looking
at a stolen body.

00:07:04,527 --> 00:07:06,329
We're looking at murder.

00:07:06,329 --> 00:07:09,599
Well, the prep chefs left
at 9:00, so the murder must have

00:07:09,599 --> 00:07:12,969
happened after that.

00:07:12,969 --> 00:07:15,171
You know, these gel mats
can hold an impression

00:07:15,171 --> 00:07:16,406
for up to 12 hours.

00:07:16,406 --> 00:07:18,742
Very close to
the blood pool.

00:07:18,742 --> 00:07:21,377
Maybe we can I.D. the
last person who stepped on it.

00:07:26,649 --> 00:07:28,485
Might be our killer.

00:07:30,553 --> 00:07:33,857
You've heard how Jesus
turned water into wine.

00:07:33,857 --> 00:07:37,494
Now watch in amazement
as I turn blood

00:07:37,494 --> 00:07:38,862
into caviar.

00:07:38,862 --> 00:07:41,464
