to Jesus?

00:07:41,464 --> 00:07:42,599
Wow.

00:07:42,599 --> 00:07:44,400
First, I take the blood

00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:46,803
and add it to a mixture of...

00:07:46,803 --> 00:07:50,607
calcium glucocinate
and calcium lactate.

00:07:50,607 --> 00:07:52,375
Next, I add xanthan,

00:07:52,375 --> 00:07:55,211
a polysaccharide secreted
from the bacterium

00:07:55,211 --> 00:07:56,746
<i>Xanthomonas campestris.</i>

00:07:56,746 --> 00:07:59,816
Used as a thickening agent
in food and a stabilizing agent

00:07:59,816 --> 00:08:01,551
in makeup.

00:08:01,551 --> 00:08:03,853
I took chemistry, too.

00:08:03,853 --> 00:08:06,756
HODGES: Blend until
thoroughly dissolved.

00:08:06,756 --> 00:08:08,625
(chuckles)

00:08:08,625 --> 00:08:10,760
I take my handy pipette,

00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,896
extract some of
the blood mixture

00:08:12,896 --> 00:08:15,298
and drop it into the alginate
one drop at a time.

00:08:19,736 --> 00:08:23,306
I will pull the sphere
from the alginate,

00:08:23,306 --> 00:08:25,642
plunge it into an ice-cold
water bath

00:08:25,642 --> 00:08:28,945
and...

00:08:28,945 --> 00:08:30,914
<i>buon appetito.</i>

00:08:30,914 --> 00:08:33,416
(chuckles)
