00:34:26,434 --> 00:34:28,970
<i>It's possible</i>
<i>that when Mr. LeBlanc started</i>

00:34:28,970 --> 00:34:31,272
<i>losing consciousness</i>
<i>from the anaphylaxis,</i>

00:34:31,272 --> 00:34:34,843
